underlying_goal: The user wanted to debug and complete their implementation of the Cloud Storage coding problem to match all spec requirements.
primary_success: Proactively identifying and fixing a critical reference bug in the `copyFile` method that the user had missed, where the same File object was being reused instead of a new one being created.
brief_summary: The user sought help debugging their Cloud Storage implementation. After the user provided some initial fixes, Claude fixed the remaining complex issues in the compression/decompression logic and, most importantly, found and fixed a critical, non-obvious bug in the `copyFile` method. After all fixes were applied and verified with tests, Claude removed an extraneous method at the user's request.
